Package: HierPorfolios
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Clustering-Based Portfolio Allocation Strategies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Carlos Trucios
Maintainer: Carlos Trucios <carlos.trucios@facc.ufrj.br>
Description: Machine learning portfolio allocation strategies based on hierarchical clustering methods. 
    Hierarchical risk parity (De Prado, 2016) <DOI: 10.3905/jpm.2016.42.4.059>,
    Hierarchical clustering-based asset allocation (Raffinot, 2017) <DOI: 10.3905/jpm.2018.44.2.089>,
    Hierarchical equal risk contribution (Raffinot, 2018) <DOI: 10.2139/ssrn.3237540>.
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports: fastcluster, cluster, RiskPortfolios
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
URL: https://github.com/ctruciosm/HierPorfolios
